{
  "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "一条线是一维，一个正方形是二维，那这个坑坑洼洼的分形呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "它比线更满，又填不满一块面积，维数似乎卡在中间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "为了给它一个确切的数，我们需要一把新的尺子，叫盒维数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "boxcount",
      "line_id": "box-1",
      "filename": "boxcount-box-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/boxcount-box-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "方法很朴素：拿边长为 ε 的方格网盖住整个图形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "boxcount",
      "line_id": "box-2",
      "filename": "boxcount-box-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/boxcount-box-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "数一数有多少个格子里落着分形的点，记作 N(ε)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "boxcount",
      "line_id": "box-3",
      "filename": "boxcount-box-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/boxcount-box-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "空格子不算，只有沾到图形的格子才计入。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "scale",
      "line_id": "scale-1",
      "filename": "scale-scale-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/scale-scale-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "把格子变小，ε 减半，非空格子数就会成倍增加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "scale",
      "line_id": "scale-2",
      "filename": "scale-scale-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/scale-scale-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "对直线，格子减半数目翻一倍；对面片，减半会翻四倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "scale",
      "line_id": "scale-3",
      "filename": "scale-scale-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/scale-scale-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.78,
      "size": 44496,
      "text": "分形介于两者之间，N(ε) 大致按 (1/ε) 的某个幂次增长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "loglog",
      "line_id": "log-1",
      "filename": "loglog-log-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/loglog-log-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "把每个尺度的 log(1/ε) 和 log N(ε) 画成散点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "loglog",
      "line_id": "log-2",
      "filename": "loglog-log-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/loglog-log-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "这些点几乎排成一条直线，它的斜率就是盒维数 D。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "loglog",
      "line_id": "log-3",
      "filename": "loglog-log-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/loglog-log-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "谢尔宾斯基三角形的斜率约等于 1.585，也就是 log3 除以 log2。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "切换不同的 ε，看左边网格变密、非空格子变多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "再看右边的散点如何贴合那条拟合直线，斜率始终稳定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "盒维数用不同尺度的方格覆盖分形，数出 N(ε)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "log N 对 log(1/ε) 的直线斜率，就是这个分数维数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "box-counting-dimension",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/box-counting-dimension/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "原来维数也能不是整数，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
